──[ Summary ]───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────//───

    Fullstack engineer with 6+ years building data-intensive fintech
    platforms, trading infrastructure, and production AI applications.
    Combines strong quantitative finance experience — automated
    liquidation bots for a Liquity-fork lending protocol, stablecoin
    platforms processing $8M+ in emerging markets, real-time financial
    dashboards for trading desks — with deep AI/LLM engineering
    (LangChain, RAG, model deployment). Recently built an energy
    intelligence platform for Vaca Muerta (Petrodata.ar) with automated
    data pipelines and executive dashboards. Strong data analysis with
    Python, SQL, and time-series modeling.

──[ Experience ]────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────//───

    Petrodata.ar (Buenos Aires, Argentina)
    2025 · Creator — Energy Data Intelligence

        Built automated Python ETL pipelines ingesting production, well,
        and pricing data from Argentina's Secretaría de Energía (CKAN
        API) into a star-schema Postgres model — 80 operators, 85K+
        wells, 327K monthly records. Integrated live market data (Brent,
        WTI, Henry Hub via EIA API), FX rates, and rig counts into a
        unified data layer for energy trading analytics. NestJS REST API
        + React/Next.js dashboards with animated KPIs, trend analysis,
        and geospatial well maps.

    W3G / Inspirae.ai — Nini (nonarcisai / getnini.ai) (Remote)
    2025 — Present · Full-Stack Developer & PM — AI Application

        Led development of a live consumer AI app (iOS/Android): React
        Native frontend, Node.js microservices on GCP, LangChain/Python
        AI pipelines for behavioral analysis. Managed team of 3 while
        hands-on in code. Deployed production LLM inference pipelines
        with RAG, structured output, and prompt iteration — serving
        thousands of users.

    VaultTech (Remote)
    2024 — 2025 · Full Stack Engineer — Lending & Vault Infrastructure
                  (Liquity fork — NDA)

        Built an automated liquidation bot and event-driven indexing
        system (subgraphs/GraphQL) for a DeFi lending protocol —
        monitoring vault collateralization, triggering liquidations, and
        managing financial risk in real time. Architected the lending
        product from scratch: Node.js backend, smart contract
        integration, and React/TypeScript dashboards for vault health
        and liquidity risk used daily by the operations desk.

    Num Finance (now Twin Finance) (Buenos Aires, Argentina)
    2023 — 2024 · Full Stack Engineer — Stablecoins & Payments

        Built fullstack products for USD- and FX-pegged stablecoins
        across Argentina, Brazil, and Mexico — $8M+ in cross-border
        volume — plus back-office tooling and REST APIs for
        Pix-to-stablecoin settlement. Created onchain data dashboards
        tracking supply, liquidity, peg health, and product KPIs across
        multiple chains, used daily by finance and strategy teams.

    Mangos Wallet (mangos.finance) (Remote)
    2022 — 2023 · Software Engineer — Consumer Wallet Platform

        Led end-to-end build of a wallet for underbanked users (React,
        TypeScript, Node.js): Web2 social-login over account-abstraction
        with integrated yield protocols (AAVE), shipping MVP to
        production for non-crypto-native users.

    Perro en la Luna (Buenos Aires / Remote)
    2021 — 2022 · Software Engineer Intern

        Client-facing apps, internal tools, and automated dashboards.
        Next.js frontend, Nest.js backend.

